  "detailed_description": "Welcome to Stumble and Fall, where chaos reigns and stumbling into victory is just as likely as falling flat on your face! Gather your friends and embark on a riotous multiplayer adventure that will have you laughing and cheering your way to victory.<br><br><i><strong>Gameplay:</strong></i><br>Stumble and Fall is a party style beat 'em up. Embrace the madness as you stumble, trip, and flail your way through wild battles in a variety of unique arenas.<br><br><i><strong>Features:</strong></i><br><br><strong>Dynamic Arenas</strong>: Battle across dynamic arenas filled with obstacles, hazards, and interactive elements. From slippery ice to chaotic collapsing caves, every location is a playground for hilarious moments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/8d394b51794ff8f677e531c59bafbf91.poster.avif?t=1715374994\" width=620 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/8d394b51794ff8f677e531c59bafbf91.webm?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/8d394b51794ff8f677e531c59bafbf91.mp4?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Local Multiplayer Madness:</strong> Round up your friends and dive into the chaos with local multiplayer support for up to 3 players. Whether you're engaging in fierce one-on-one duels or chaotic free-for-alls, Stumble and Fall promises laughter-filled fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/4c19b1800a558fa127666823c78a4d51.poster.avif?t=1715374994\" width=620 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/4c19b1800a558fa127666823c78a4d51.webm?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/4c19b1800a558fa127666823c78a4d51.mp4?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Customization Options:</strong> Personalize your warriors with a small amount of costumes and accessories (Lots more will be added in near updates!). Mix and match to assert your dominance in style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/a3025a38e5e4c16fac6eb06387dd767a.poster.avif?t=1715374994\" width=620 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/a3025a38e5e4c16fac6eb06387dd767a.webm?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/a3025a38e5e4c16fac6eb06387dd767a.mp4?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "Welcome to Stumble and Fall, where chaos reigns and stumbling into victory is just as likely as falling flat on your face! Gather your friends and embark on a riotous multiplayer adventure that will have you laughing and cheering your way to victory.<br><br><i><strong>Gameplay:</strong></i><br>Stumble and Fall is a party style beat 'em up. Embrace the madness as you stumble, trip, and flail your way through wild battles in a variety of unique arenas.<br><br><i><strong>Features:</strong></i><br><br><strong>Dynamic Arenas</strong>: Battle across dynamic arenas filled with obstacles, hazards, and interactive elements. From slippery ice to chaotic collapsing caves, every location is a playground for hilarious moments.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/8d394b51794ff8f677e531c59bafbf91.poster.avif?t=1715374994\" width=620 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/8d394b51794ff8f677e531c59bafbf91.webm?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/8d394b51794ff8f677e531c59bafbf91.mp4?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Local Multiplayer Madness:</strong> Round up your friends and dive into the chaos with local multiplayer support for up to 3 players. Whether you're engaging in fierce one-on-one duels or chaotic free-for-alls, Stumble and Fall promises laughter-filled fun.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/4c19b1800a558fa127666823c78a4d51.poster.avif?t=1715374994\" width=620 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/4c19b1800a558fa127666823c78a4d51.webm?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/4c19b1800a558fa127666823c78a4d51.mp4?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Customization Options:</strong> Personalize your warriors with a small amount of costumes and accessories (Lots more will be added in near updates!). Mix and match to assert your dominance in style.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/a3025a38e5e4c16fac6eb06387dd767a.poster.avif?t=1715374994\" width=620 height=106 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/a3025a38e5e4c16fac6eb06387dd767a.webm?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2958960/extras/a3025a38e5e4c16fac6eb06387dd767a.mp4?t=1715374994\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
